  <!-- Testimonials Widget *********** -->

  <Testimonials
    title="Testimonials"
    subtitle="Discover what my colleagues have to say about their experiences working with me."
    testimonials={[
      {
        testimonial: `I had the pleasure of working with Ved during their internship at Google. They demonstrated a strong eagerness to learn and quickly adapted to new tasks. Their communication skills were noteworthy, as they consistently articulated their ideas and progress clearly, which greatly facilitated team collaboration. I can say that Ved will excel in any future role they pursue, as they have shown the capability during their time with us.`,
